002package com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common;
003
004import java.util.function.Function;
005
006import com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.*;
007
008public class UpdateQueryBuilderDsl {
009    public UpdateQueryBuilderDsl() {
010    }
011
012    public static UpdateQueryBuilderDsl of() {
013        return new UpdateQueryBuilderDsl();
014    }
015
016    public LongComparisonPredicateBuilder<UpdateQueryBuilderDsl> version() {
017        return new LongComparisonPredicateBuilder<>(
018            BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("version")),
019            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, UpdateQueryBuilderDsl::of));
020    }
021
022    public CombinationQueryPredicate<UpdateQueryBuilderDsl> actions(
023            Function<com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.UpdateActionQueryBuilderDsl, CombinationQueryPredicate<com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.UpdateActionQueryBuilderDsl>> fn) {
024        return new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(
025            ContainerQueryPredicate.of()
026                    .parent(ConstantQueryPredicate.of().constant("actions"))
027                    .inner(fn.apply(com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.UpdateActionQueryBuilderDsl.of())),
028            UpdateQueryBuilderDsl::of);
029    }
030
031    public CollectionPredicateBuilder<UpdateQueryBuilderDsl> actions() {
032        return new CollectionPredicateBuilder<>(BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("actions")),
033            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, UpdateQueryBuilderDsl::of));
034    }
035
036}
